{"tid":1249553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"621最大功臣：燒山","createTime":"2019-06-21T18:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:12:02.000Z","uid":247085,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2992a74f34e1b2a4f4670f76e542e3609e417260","tid":1249553,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山，燒山好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大學生又吹雞群眾運動，這是非常魯莽。<br />\n吹雞不能不停進行，號召群眾運動前應深化社區而不能不斷進行。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭要有策略，有所進退，要柔un，慢慢就會成功。<br />\n<br />\n因為現在已經係階段性勝利，要返回社區做深化勝利的工作，在這一方面民陣是非常好。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭有好多方式，不一定是衝擊，可以做社區不合作運動，或者集體自首，這方面政府不能武力鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n相反如果是勇武衝擊，代價非常大，隨時俾人告暴動罪，警方武力又會再升級，最終你係一定唔夠佢打。<br />\n<br />\n面對殘暴政權，更應使用和理非對抗，因為佢隨時可以殺咗你，甘地面對是一個非常殘暴的殖民地政府，佢都用左10幾年先成功，你哋以為621一日就成功？"},{"pid":"243e7eec5434287a3b2520e3c685c6eff30c8205","tid":1249553,"uid":23037,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"燒山成功曲線挽救運動"},{"pid":"df65562b5479cb07254d0e5bb73268f60b701e84","tid":1249553,"uid":247085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"243e7eec5434287a3b2520e3c685c6eff30c8205","tid":1249553,"uid":23037,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"燒山成功曲線挽救運動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"真，本身今朝仲以為冇料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a903e56668218ec2aea066418c7a048869fadd8","tid":1249553,"uid":1876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca74f299a794fbd27fb3dfa43e3bd8ebc7dc8f59","tid":1249553,"uid":20282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20